==English==

===Noun===
'''pimp''' (''plural:'' '''[[pimps]]''')

# A person who [[solicit]]s customers for [[prostitution]] and acts as manager for [[prostitute]]s; a [[panderer]].
#:''The '''pimp''' beat one of his girls up for not making enough money in one night.''
# (''slang, [[w:AAVE|AAVE]]'') Man who can easily attract women; a [[player]]/[[playa]].

